---

Portions of this project (the Parallax Occlusion Mapping shader) are
ported from DepthFlow's depthflow.glsl. The original algorithm implements
ray marching with forward/backward refinement passes for depth surface
intersection. Our adaptation modifies the shader for WebGL/Three.js
compatibility, adds wave wipe transitions, metallic edge glow, spotlight,
atmospheric effects, and per-painting special effects (video texture,
breathing glow, mouse-triggered spark).
